urdu transliteration text:
hai maa ko yaqeen tum maa ki baat rakhoge, ye yaad rahe qaimo may hai pyase bachedarya pe agar jaana ho seh roz ke pyaso, tum pyas na bujhana ay auno-mohamad
O Aun & Muhammad
